snippet.title: Have You Scene It Podcast
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Have You Scene It Podcast Channel!
Two movie fanatics giving their reviews on the latest films in the box office, what to watch on streaming services, and giving their reviews each week. 
HySi Productions
